    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"互相 expresses "},{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"reciprocal action where both parties give and receive equally"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":". It's used for:"}],"type":"paragraph"},
    {"children":[{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mutual help"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 互相帮助 (hùxiāng bāngzhù) - \"help each other\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reciprocal respect"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 互相尊重 (hùxiāng zūnzhòng) - \"respect each other\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mutual understanding"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 互相理解 (hùxiāng lǐjiě) - \"understand each other\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Two-way communication"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 互相交流 (hùxiāng jiāoliú) - \"communicate with each other\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"}],"ordered":true,"spread":false,"start":1,"type":"list"},
